{"tid":1450153,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《突發》連登巴絲一人一post 狂開！","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:02.000Z","uid":269203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"080d36eba0f59ba643d0c48f2e162bc6011853b2","tid":1450153,"uid":269203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=aec8592e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=75f3b463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"5eb22e75382ead9ccdf554715a8d61d5f49addf3","tid":1450153,"uid":269203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"連擊10吓！"},{"pid":"2f141eda05e849c09c97fa867b0c428f303a799c","tid":1450153,"uid":269203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a34088ac2dc47fe91ee7414ae709718235cd12","tid":1450153,"uid":269203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\